He's got a hidden ability!

44
00:01:57,970 --> 00:02:02,350
It's an ability called Bites the Dust,
and it can blow away time!

45
00:02:04,370 --> 00:02:09,840
Episode 39    Goodbye, Morioh – The Heart of Gold

46
